This test computes the 1D PDR structure for the parameters corresponding to the benchmark tests presented in Rollig et al. 2007.
The default test is the V1 test in Rollig et al. 2007. You can modify the ntot and chi to do a different one.
The setup_Rollig_test.py will automatically change the H2 formation rate on grains to one identical to the test. This is done automatically when running make. 
Result files for the PDR codes in the project are available here: https://lecture.ph1.uni-koeln.de/pdr-comparison/results_data_post.htm
